<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Wikipedia says:<br/>&quot;It is published by Hodder &amp; Stoughton in Britain under the title McGee on Food and Cooking: An Encyclopedia of Kitchen Science, Histor<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Wikipedia says:<br />"It is published by Hodder &amp; Stoughton in Britain under the title McGee on Food and Cooking: An Encyclopedia of Kitchen Science, History and Culture."<br />But I'd like to know if there are any content differences.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
