        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1466833978" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11385424055981413794">This book is a MUST for the kitchen. I was never one for math, chemistry or any sort of science until I started cooking. This book is a great resource and packed tight with incredibly interesting food knowledge.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

